data.description: Come and check out this home on a half acre lot and 4 BAY GARAGE in Donegal School district located off the beaten path in the small village of Rowenna!  Within minutes from the Susquehanna river and trail! There are 4 bedrooms, 1 has a privacy violation. 2 of those bedrooms are located on the main level along with laundry. 1 full bathroom which was renovated last year. A brand new heat pump system will be installed prior to settlement once a contract has been accepted.  All windows have been replaced within the last 6 years, minus 2 in the living room which have been ordered. Schedule a showing today and start the new year in your new home!
